#include<iostream>

using namespace std;

int sum(int n)
{

   int sum=0;

   while(n!=0)
   {

     sum=sum+n%10;
     n=n/10;

   }

   return sum;

}

int main()
{

   int t,count,l,u,i,j;
   cin>>t;

   int prime[100]={0};

   prime[0]=1;
   prime[1]=1;

   for(i=2;i<100;i++)
   {

     for(j=2;i*j<100;j++)
     prime[i*j]=1;

   }

   while(t--)
   {

     cin>>l>>u;

     count=0;

     for(i=l;i<=u;i++)
     {

       if(prime[sum(i)]==0)
       count++;

     }

     cout<<count<<endl;

   }

   return 0;

}
